\details{
Internal R6 generator backing \code{\link[=seq_highlight]{seq_highlight()}}. Inherits from
\code{\link{SeqLinkR6}}. Draws a continuous filled highlight band that passes
through every track from \code{t0} down to \code{t1} (inclusive). Per-track
